9c1e81a9-1f9d-4052-a764-da6957e7761e.title: Master smithing tutor
9c1e81a9-1f9d-4052-a764-da6957e7761e.text:
Well met! Are you interested in hearing about the art
of smithing?

options.text: How can I train my smithing?
What kinds of things can I smith?

c51875cb-805c-408b-ad59-68b1028be6bd.title: Master smithing tutor
c51875cb-805c-408b-ad59-68b1028be6bd.text:
Well, just come back any time you want to know
anything!

7ac7a38c-3b5a-4099-ad4a-3cc5cc618a2c.title: <player>
7ac7a38c-3b5a-4099-ad4a-3cc5cc618a2c.text: What kinds of things can I smith?

060cc265-e6e4-4b73-99ea-6430119c9dc8.title: Master smithing tutor
060cc265-e6e4-4b73-99ea-6430119c9dc8.text:
There are many things you can make, from weapons to
your good old fashioned armour.

9fbef86a-2d50-4c44-bfb5-65ad426a535b.title: Master smithing tutor
9fbef86a-2d50-4c44-bfb5-65ad426a535b.text:
Weapons are the cheapest things to smith. They range
from a measly one bar, all the way to three bars.

0598b17c-96f2-41fc-a705-784ab926621d.title: Master smithing tutor
0598b17c-96f2-41fc-a705-784ab926621d.text:
Armour can be the costliest item to smith, the cost of
each item ranges from a measly one bar all the way up
to a whopping five bars.

63532e78-4432-4a96-a969-2334cadf36ea.title: Master smithing tutor
63532e78-4432-4a96-a969-2334cadf36ea.text:
Some weapons and armour, such as darts, will require
you to have gained knowledge on how to smith them.
This is due to the complex nature of the weapon.

56715fe8-eae7-49ad-8e36-7c2c215edcba.title: Master smithing tutor
56715fe8-eae7-49ad-8e36-7c2c215edcba.text:
You might find that other items don't require
conventional bars you would gather. Some may require
you to piece blades back together or even infuse a
crystal into a piece of armour.

3765f091-d1f2-45fa-9c2e-54df6085dbd9.title: Master smithing tutor
3765f091-d1f2-45fa-9c2e-54df6085dbd9.text: Is there anything else you want to know?

0e638cde-6c48-491a-b7f3-6463728475e5.title: <player>
0e638cde-6c48-491a-b7f3-6463728475e5.text: How can I train my smithing?

3faa2874-e59f-435d-939d-5d146cf3029e.title: Master smithing tutor
3faa2874-e59f-435d-939d-5d146cf3029e.text:
To be able to smith anything, you're going to need one
of these beauties.

15feb89d-37ab-4509-8374-797cd85db104.text: The Master Smithing tutor gives you a hammer.

8ceaf79b-f0ae-406f-b009-64398bbeb4a4.title: Master smithing tutor
8ceaf79b-f0ae-406f-b009-64398bbeb4a4.text:
You're going to need to get your hand on some metal
bars. You could do this by mining your own ores and
smelting them at a furnace.

2cd80005-7466-454d-a4ab-08bda876ca1e.title: Master smithing tutor
2cd80005-7466-454d-a4ab-08bda876ca1e.text:
There is a furnace located in Lumbridge, just north of
the castle opposite the general store.

734cb084-0d8a-4d0a-ab54-189547684a64.title: Master smithing tutor
734cb084-0d8a-4d0a-ab54-189547684a64.text:
If you are looking for some ore, there is a mine east of
Varrock. There you can find some copper and tin ore.
Don't forget to bring a pickaxe.

5174d433-15b9-461e-a890-330930077a75.title: Master smithing tutor
5174d433-15b9-461e-a890-330930077a75.text:
When you have your bars, bring them to an anvil to
open the smithing interface. If the item name is in
black, this means you do not have the level to smith the
item.

9bba9735-3f7a-4f63-8440-4f7795b48da0.title: Master smithing tutor
9bba9735-3f7a-4f63-8440-4f7795b48da0.text:
If the item name is in white, this means you do have
the level to smith the item. You will see the bars
required to smith the item underneath the name of the
item.

fe1b136d-fefd-4804-97e5-2b866983b73e.title: Master smithing tutor
fe1b136d-fefd-4804-97e5-2b866983b73e.text:
If the number of bars is in orange, this means you do
not have enough bars to smith the item. If it is in
green, this means you have enough bars for the item.

1576a54c-78e3-4331-86a8-4f5dd3dc7fcd.title: Master smithing tutor
1576a54c-78e3-4331-86a8-4f5dd3dc7fcd.text: Is there anything else you would like to know?
